==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: endangered
<hw>en*dan"gered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Being
in a condition or situation where life or serious harm is possible; in
danger; at risk.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Small in numbers, with significant possibility of
extinction; -- of species.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>endangered species</ent>⟦br⟧
